    <main>
        <section class="features">
            <h2>Why Use Network Diagram Visualizer?</h2>
            <div class="feature-item">
                <h4>📁 Upload Your Data</h4>
                <p>Easily upload Excel files containing network details to generate clear and accurate network diagrams. Our tool processes your data and presents it visually in just seconds.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-item">
                <h4>📊 Visualize Network Structures</h4>
                <p>See your network come to life with an intuitive, interactive diagram. Explore connections between devices and understand your infrastructure at a glance.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-item">
                <h4>⚡ Add Devices On-the-Fly</h4>
                <p>Quickly add new devices and connections to your diagram without re-uploading the file. Modify your network as you go for maximum flexibility.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-item">
                <h4>🖨 Save & Share</h4>
                <p>Export your diagram as a PDF for presentations or documentation. Share it with your team to improve collaboration and understanding.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>Network Diagram Visualizer © 2024</p>
    </footer>

